Aggregate sql statistic, sort and show


1) Get this : git clone https://github.com/progman/sqltop.git
2) Make this: git submodule update --init && make x64 && ./test.sh
3) Use this : sqltop SQL_STAT_FILE
4) Enjoy!


Format SQL_STAT_FILE is easy, see text file example_sql_stat

UNIXTIME MICROTIME SQL_TAG SQL_STR

UNIXTIME  - (uint64_t) time start execution sql query in unixtime, example: 1402382914
MICROTIME - (uint64_t) time execution sql query in microseconds (1/1000000 sec), example: 1
SQL_TAG   - (string)   uniq sql query name, example: SQL001
SQL_STR   - (hex string) hex encoded sql query, example: 53454c454354204e4f5728293b0a
